Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends: libnginx-mod-http-lua,
         ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends},
Recommends: nginx,
Description: Lua upstream API module for Nginx
 Exposes a Lua API for querying and manipulating Nginx upstream server
 groups at runtime. Provides ngx.upstream with functions to list upstreams,
 inspect peers, and dynamically mark peers as up or down.
 .
 Required by lua-resty-upstream-healthcheck for active health monitoring
 of upstream backends.
